	Tooltip:
		'''
		Summons a colossal decayed sea vortex at the cursor
		The vortex relentlessly draws nearby enemies in and rends them, even unraveling hostile projectiles
		Periodically hurls outward homing decayed sea orbs
		Firing again refreshes the existing vortex; on natural collapse it bursts into a ring of orbs
		"The roar of the rotting depths churned into sand"
		'''
}

