		After the charging is completed, fly towards the target.
		Right-click to perform a short-range thrust.
		'''
}

OniMachete: {
	DisplayName: Oni Machete
	Tooltip:
		'''
		When held, six oni hands will be generated to assist in combat.
		True melee attacks will release ghost flames.
		'''
}

Pandemonium: {
	DisplayName: Pandemonium
	Tooltip:
		'''
		Left-click to charge and release Transcendent Magic
		Right-click to cast a Brimstone Rune at the cursor
		Press [PandemoniumQSkill] to unleash Brimstone Judgement
		Press [PandemoniumRSkill] to perform The End of All Demons
		'''
}

Proverbs: {
	DisplayName: Proverb
	Tooltip:
		'''
		Generates a small brimstone rune behind you
		Grants immunity to most fire-based debuffs
		Most of your attacks inflict the Withered Curse debuff
		[Content]
		'''
	L1:
		'''
		Deals double damage to the Brimstone Witch; 
		her attacks have a chance to critically strike you
		'''
	L2:
		'''
		If you are reading this, then I am likely already gone.
		Throughout my long years, this ring was the only thing that felt truly cold.
		But somewhere along the way, it absorbed a mortal's warmth... and became... too hot to let go.
		I have returned to the Brimstone, reduced to the ashes of an era.
		I should have departed with nothing, 
		yet I found myself greedy for this singular warmth, wishing to preserve it.
		Wear it.
		And when you finally raise your blade against the gods...
		Know that even if the world freezes over, I will still be burning at your fingertips.
		'''
}

AncientStormGoddessSpear: {
	DisplayName: Ancient Storm Goddess Spear
	Tooltip:
		'''
		A Spear capable of sending out Fierce Lightning Kisses that bounces off enemies.
		"It is already a thing of the past, but it still works."
		[legend]
		'''
	Legend:
		'''
		Alina was once Terra’s sharpest warrior, wielding a blade of thunder to cleave through darkness, 
		her faith unwavering and absolute. But faith could not shield her from the indifference of the gods.  
		When the Supreme Deity passed judgment, her comrades, kin, oaths, and glory were reduced to ashes. 
		She witnessed firsthand how so-called justice trampled everything into dust, how order was merely a veil for the cruelest of destructions.  
		She no longer sought the light but reforged herself in the abyss. An ancient, 
		forbidden power consumed her soul, granting her strength beyond mortal comprehension.  
		Her armor became wreckage forged in the depths, her eyes burned with the remnants of thunder and darkness entwined. 
		She was no longer Terra’s guardian, but the storm itself—a vengeance that could not be stopped.  
		Her fury swept the battlefield like a howling tempest, her thunder tore through thrones and temples. 
		She fought not for justice, not for Terra, not for the gods.  
		She fought for vengeance, for annihilation—to make those who deemed themselves righteous understand the true meaning of fear.
		'''
}

ConstructionBlueprintQET: {
	DisplayName: Construction Blueprint (Quantum Entanglement Tower)
	Tooltip:
		'''
		Use to learn how to craft the [i:CalamityOverhaul/CQETConstructor] Self-Constructor
